title: YUS - Favorites Remixed (2011)
description:
Favorites Remixed is the first remix album from YUS. It was released on December 15, 2011. The cover artwork was created by Devan Romero.

Tracklist:
1. Animal Collective - My Girls (YUS Remix) 2:54
2. Crystal Castles - Violent Dreams (YUS Remix) 4:43
3. How To Dress Well - Suicide Dream 2 (YUS Remix) 6:06
4. James Blake - The Wilhelm Scream (YUS Remix) 5:35
